# Архитектурный анализ схемы — Трек 4.263 (Schema Decoupling)

> Дата: 2026-02-26 | Агент: G3H | Основан на реальной схеме PocketBase v0.36.3

---

## 1. Текущая схема (as-is)

### 1.1 Иерархия зависимостей

```
users (Coach)
  └── seasons  [coach_id required, athlete_id?, group_id?]
        └── training_phases  [season_id required]
              └── training_plans  [phase_id required ⚠️]
                    └── plan_exercises
                    └── plan_snapshots
                    └── plan_assignments  [plan_id, athlete_id?, group_id?]
                    └── training_logs

users (Coach)
  └── seasons
        └── competitions  [season_id required ⚠️]
              └── competition_participants
              └── competition_proposals
              └── competition_media
```

### 1.2 Реальные поля из PocketBase (конкретные данные)

#### `competitions`
| Поле | Тип | Required | Примечание |
|------|-----|----------|------------|
| [id](file:///Users/bogdan/antigravity/skills%20master/tf/src/lib/pocketbase/types.ts#321-327) | text(15) | ✅ system | PK |
| `name` | text(255) | ✅ | |
| [date](file:///Users/bogdan/antigravity/skills%20master/tf/src/lib/pocketbase/services/competitions.ts#86-92) | date | ✅ | |
| `priority` | select | ✅ | A/B/C |
| `season_id` | relation→seasons | ✅ **required=true** | **⚠️ Блокирует онбординг** |
| `discipline` | select | ❌ | high_jump/long_jump/triple_jump |
| `season_type` | select | ❌ | indoor/outdoor |
| `website` | text(1000) | ❌ | |
| `status` | select | ❌ | planned/confirmed/completed/cancelled |
| `official_result` | number | ❌ | метры |
| `official_updated_by` | relation→users | ❌ | |
| `official_updated_at` | date | ❌ | |
| `location` | text(500) | ❌ | |
| `notes` | text(2000) | ❌ | |
| `deleted_at` | date | ❌ | SoftDelete |

**Индексы на competitions:**
```sql
CREATE INDEX idx_comp_season ON competitions (season_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_comp_filters ON competitions (season_id, date, discipline, season_type, status);
```

**API Rules (competitions):**
```
listRule:   season_id.coach_id = authId || season_id.athlete_id.user_id = authId || season_id.group_id.group_members...
createRule: season_id.coach_id = authId || season_id.athlete_id.user_id = authId
```
> **Критический изъян:** весь доступ завязан на `season_id` — без сезона правило вернёт false.

---

#### `training_plans`
| Поле | Тип | Required | Примечание |
|------|-----|----------|------------|
| `phase_id` | relation→training_phases | ✅ **required=true** | **⚠️ Цепочка 4 JOIN** |
| `week_number` | number(1-52) | ✅ | |
| `status` | select | ✅ | draft/published/archived |
| `notes` | text(5000) | ❌ | |
| `sync_id` | text(36) | ❌ | UUID для offline sync |
| `deleted_at` | date | ❌ | SoftDelete |
| `athlete_id` | relation→athletes | ❌ | **Уже есть — для overrides!** |
| `parent_plan_id` | relation→training_plans | ❌ | Self-ref для overrides |
| `day_notes` | json | ❌ | {"1": "Mon note", ...} |

**Индекс:**
```sql
CREATE INDEX idx_plans_phase ON training_plans (phase_id);
```

**API Rules (training_plans):**
```
listRule:   phase_id.season_id.coach_id = authId || athlete_id.user_id = authId
createRule: phase_id.season_id.coach_id = authId  ← только тренер через фазу!
viewRule:   + plan_assignments_via_plan_id.athlete_id.user_id ?= authId
```
> **Проблема:** атлет не может создать свой план, даже ad-hoc.

---

#### `plan_assignments` (уже полиморфный — хорошее решение!)
| Поле | Тип | Required |
|------|-----|----------|
| `plan_id` | relation→training_plans (cascadeDelete=true) | ✅ |
| `athlete_id` | relation→athletes | ❌ |
| `group_id` | relation→groups | ❌ |
| `status` | select(active/inactive) | ❌ |

**6 индексов включая UNIQUE partial:**
```sql
UNIQUE (plan_id, athlete_id) WHERE status='active' AND athlete_id != ''
UNIQUE (plan_id, group_id) WHERE status='active' AND group_id != ''
```
> ✅ `plan_assignments` уже умеет полиморфное владение — это можно переиспользовать!

---

#### `seasons` (для справки)
| Поле | Тип | Required |
|------|-----|----------|
| `coach_id` | relation→users | ✅ |
| `athlete_id` | relation→athletes | ❌ |
| `group_id` | relation→groups | ❌ |
| `name` | text | ✅ |
| `start_date` | date | ✅ |
| `end_date` | date | ✅ |
| `deleted_at` | date | ❌ |

> Seasons уже поддерживает athlete_id и group_id — но сезон как контейнер всё равно обязателен.

